<div class="title">A Thought</div>
<div class="substance">Ayahuasca (B. caapi)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=J.+Langdon&Exact=1">J. Langdon</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; J. Langdon. "A Thought: An Experience with Ayahuasca (B. caapi) (exp1776)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jun 13, 1995. erowid.org/exp/1776</div>

